<div id="midheader">
	<div id="midcontent">
		<div id="mission">
			<h1>Welcome to CitrusDB.org</h1>
			Our mission is to provide an open source 
			customer database and billing software solution that 
			can be used in many different service industries, 
			including internet service, consulting, webhosting, 
			telecommunications, and voip. 
			<p>	
			CitrusDB is a web based customer database and billing 
			software solution that uses PHP and a database 
			backend (MySQL)   
			to keep track of customer information, CRM, services, 
			products, billing invoices and credit cards, and 
			customer service information.  It is licensed under 
			the GPL version 2 open source license.	
		</div>
		<div id="screenshot">
			<img src="images/screenshot.jpg">
			<br>
			<center>
				<a style="color: darkgreen; font-weight: bold;" href="download/citrus-0.9.2.tar.gz">Get the Latest Release<br><b style="font-size: 10pt;">Version 0.9.2 (996k)</b></a>
			</center>
		</div>
